data.eml:eml: Seabird Atlas of South-eastern Australian Waters 1975-1993

Seabird Atlas of South-eastern Australian Waters derived from multiple sources. Data from paper by Reid, T.A., Hindell, M.A., Eades, D.W. and Newman, M. 2002 Seabird Atlas of South-eastern Australian Waters, Birds Australia Monograph 4, Birds Australia, Melbourne. The following surveys/voyages have been removed as they exist in the existing OBIS dataset ANARE WoV - WOCE91, geosci , 1988/89 v4, 1989/90 v3, fishog and Thirst
